### RescueGuide API - InstructionCategory Controller Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5238/api/instructioncategory

### Get all instruction categories
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get instruction category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Get instruction category by ID (non-existent)
GET {{baseUrl}}/999

### Create new instruction category
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 6,
  "name": "Erste Hilfe bei Verbrennungen",
  "description": "Anleitung zur Behandlung von Verbrennungen",
  "steps": []
}

### Create another instruction category
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 7,
  "name": "Erste Hilfe bei Schnittwunden",
  "description": "Anleitung zur Behandlung von Schnittwunden",
  "steps": []
}

### Update instruction category
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Erste Hilfe bei Verbrennungen - Aktualisiert",
  "description": "Aktualisierte Anleitung zur Behandlung von Verbrennungen",
  "steps": []
}

### Delete instruction category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1

### Delete non-existent instruction category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/999

### Update non-existent instruction category
PUT {{baseUrl}}/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 999,
  "name": "Test Category",
  "description": "Test Description",
  "steps": []
}

